AB  - This article presents the construction of a semantic knowledge graph of the open data of legal entities (SKG:CNPJ). SKG:CNPJ is obtained from the semantic integration of four data sources: RFB, IBGE, Correios, TCU and CEIS. The main objective of SKG:CNPJ is to provide a semantic layer, so that applications can have integrated access to the data source data through the Semantic Layer. The data and metadata of the SKG:CNPJ are made available on a Semantic Portal (Semantic-CNPJ) for query and visualization. The article also describes the use of SKG:CNPJ for construction of semantic queries. © 2022 Copyright for this paper by its authors.
