AB  - The Scholarly Question Answering over Linked Data (Scholarly QALD) 1 at The International Semantic Web Conference (ISWC) 2023 challenge presents two sub-tasks to tackle question answering (QA) over knowledge graphs (KGs). We answer the KGQA over DBLP (DBLP-QuAD) task by proposing a neurosymbolic (NS) framework based on PSYCHIC 2, an extractive QA model capable of identifying the query and entities related to a KG question. Our system achieved a F1 score of 00.18% on question answering and came in third place for entity linking (EL) with a score of 71.00%. © 2023 CEUR-WS. All rights reserved.
