AB  - In order to optimize and improve the fast translation of complex English sentences, this paper proposes a fast translation method of complex English sentences based on artificial intelligence semantic text analysis model. A semantic structure parameter analysis model for rapid translation of English complex sentences is established, and quantitative feature analysis is carried out for rapid translation of English-Chinese complex sentences to obtain a quality analysis scale for rapid translation of English-Chinese complex sentences. The fuzzy decision-making method is adopted to comprehensively investigate the semantic features of sentences and the cognitive features of subjects, and a language cognitive perception model for rapid translation of complex English sentences is established. Through pattern analysis of language syntactic structure, semantic parameters are configured in the semantic text analysis model of artificial intelligence, which forms a text parameter analysis model for rapid translation of complex English sentences. The test results show that the scale analysis ability of this method for rapid translation of English-Chinese complex sentences is strong, the evaluation results are accurate and reliable, and the accuracy of rapid translation of English complex sentences is improved.
