AB  - With the rapid development of artificial intelligence technology, computer algorithms are playing an increasingly important role in the field of higher education. By introducing computer algorithm thinking into the discipline construction of universities, students' logical analysis ability, problem-solving ability, and innovative thinking can be effectively cultivated. Algorithmic thinking training can significantly enhance students' critical thinking skills and promote interdisciplinary knowledge integration. Based on the analysis of relevant research, this paper explores the specific application strategies and implementation paths of computer algorithms in promoting critical thinking cultivation, providing new ideas and methods for the construction of disciplines in universities, which is of great significance for improving the quality of education and teaching.
