AB  - In the process of oral English learning, oral assessment can make students understand their oral problems and correct them. The traditional manual assessment is low in efficiency, high in cost, and has many limitations. However, the automatic assessment of spoken English can be realized with the help of artificial intelligence technology, which is an important reform direction for the future oral English teaching and evaluation. This article introduces the principle of automatic oral English assessment based on artificial intelligence technology, and discusses the feasibility of using artificial intelligence technology to partially replace manual scoring in oral English assessment, exploring the way to improve the stability and objectivity of assessment by using artificial intelligence technology, discussing the application of artificial intelligence technology in oral English autonomous learning, and also putting forward some suggestions on how to further improve the accuracy of artificial intelligence scoring in oral English assessment.
